<bibRefCitation author="Csiki" box="[573,724,1101,1127]" pageId="6" pageNumber="20" refString="Csiki, E. (1934) Coleopterorum Catalogus auspiciis et auxilio W. Junk editus a S. Schenkling. Pars 134. Curculionidae: subfam. Cleoninae. Junk, Berlin, 152 p." type="book" year="1934">
